# Copy this file to .env and paste ONE key. NEVER commit .env.
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# The backend auto-selects a provider: OpenRouter is checked first, then Claude.
# With no key set, the app still works using its built-in offline engine.

# --- Option A: OpenRouter (has FREE models) ---------------------------------
# Get a key at https://openrouter.ai/keys  (free tier available)
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-your-key-here
# OPENROUTER_MODEL=meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct:free

# --- Option B: Claude -------------------------------------------------------
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
